The paper deals with the analysis of data sets with multiple entity and feature types as well as their relationships, which is a common theme in social network analysis (cs.SI) and data mining (cs.SD). The paper proposes a new approach for community detection in heterogeneous multilayer networks, which is a topic of interest in systems and control (cs.SY), as well as in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer science (cs.DS).
